Project Title: US Healthcare Dynamics Dashboard

Description:
The US Healthcare Dynamics Dashboard is a Power BI data visualization project designed to analyze healthcare trends and patient-related data across different regions in the United States. The dashboard provides insights into patient demographics, treatment costs, hospital performance, and healthcare utilization.

Dataset Includes:

Patient demographics

Hospital details

Treatment costs

Admission and discharge data

Regional healthcare statistics

Tools Used:

Power BI

Microsoft Excel

Power Query

Features:

Region-wise healthcare analysis

Patient demographic insights

Treatment cost visualization

Interactive charts, filters, and KPIs for better data exploration

Outcome:
This dashboard helps healthcare organizations and analysts understand healthcare trends, identify patterns in patient care, and support better decision-making using data-driven insights
